Package org.readlogsfirst.api.logreader.logitemparser

Interface Summary
ContentBuildingStrategy<T extends Comparable<T>> Finally builds the log line from the tokens
IndexFindingStrategy<T> Strategy used to extract the index from a list of tokens.
LineFixerStrategy Normalize common issues in log lines (like badly formatted lines) when possible
LineTokenizerStrategy Splits a log line given as a string into tokens.
LogItemParser Log item parser get a log item as a String and parse it producing a LogLine object.
 

Class Summary
LogParserBuilder<T extends Comparable<T>> This is used to build the parser.
LogParserContext<T extends Comparable<T>> A generic parser that uses four strategies to build up a LogLine structure.
LogParserContextTest Tests a strategy based log parser
TimestampIndexParse This parser generates unstructured log lines with a date as index.
TimestampParserTest Perfors some parsing tests for timestamp parser
 

Exception Summary
LogItemParsingException Points out an issue in parsing.
